Package me.normanmaurer.niosmtp.delivery.chain

Interface Summary
SMTPClientFutureListenerFactory A Factory which is responsible for return the right SMTPClientFutureListener depending on the state of the SMTPClientSession and the SMTPRequest or SMTPMessage
 

Class Summary
AbstractAuthResponseListener Abstract base class of ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener which AUTH callbacks should use
AbstractPipeliningResponseListener ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener implementation which should get sub-classed by implementations which may be used within the PIPELINING context.
AuthLoginResponseListener AbstractAuthResponseListener which handles AUTH LOGIN
AuthPlainResponseListener AbstractAuthResponseListener which should be used to handle AUTH PLAIN
ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener<E> Abstract base implementation of SMTPClientFutureListener which completes the SMTPClientFuture on an Exception
DataResponseListener ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener implementation which will handle the DATA SMTPResponse It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPClientFutureListener added.
EhloResponseListener ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener implementation which will handle the EHLO SMTPResponse It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPClientFutureListener added.
LMTPClientFutureListenerFactoryImpl SMTPClientFutureListenerFactoryImpl implementation which returns the SMTPClientFutureListener's while processing the LMTP Transaction
LMTPPostDataResponseCallback ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener which handles the SMTPResponse for the DATA finish sequence in the LMTP protocol
LMTPWelcomeResponseListener ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener which will be used after the welcome SMTPResponse was sent from the LMTP Server
MailResponseListener ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener implementation which will handle the MAIL SMTPResponse It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPClientFutureListener added.
PostDataResponseListener ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener implementation which will handle the POST DATA SMTPResponse which will get send after the SMTPMessage get submitted via the CRLF.CRLF sequence
RcptResponseListener ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener implementation which will handle the RCPT SMTPResponse It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPClientFutureListener added.
SMTPClientFutureListenerFactoryImpl  
StartTlsResponseListener ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener implementation which will handle the STARTLS SMTPResponse It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right StartTlsResponseListener added.
WelcomeResponseListener ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener implementation which will handle the WELCOME SMTPResponse which is triggered after the connection is established to the SMTP Server It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPClientFutureListener added.
